<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Refund Issued as Spare Change</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 30px;">
    <h1 style="color: #2563eb; margin-top: 0;">Refund Issued as Spare Change</h1>
    
    <p>Your refund has been issued as Spare Change to your Cheap eSIMs account.</p>
    
    <div style="background-color: white; border-radius: 6px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: 600; width: 40%;">Order ID:</td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{orderId}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: 600;">Refund Amount:</td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-size: 18px; color: #2563eb; font-weight: 700;">{{refundAmountFormatted}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: 600;">New Spare Change Balance:</td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #2563eb; font-weight: 600;">{{spareChangeBalanceFormatted}}</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>
    
    <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 20px;">
      Your Spare Change is now available and can be used for future Cheap eSIMs purchases.
    </p>
    
    <div style="margin-top: 30px; text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #2563eb; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600;">View Spare Change Balance</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

